==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Garner
<hw>Gar"ner</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Garnered</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Garnering</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To gather for preservation; to
